short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Easily access your current Github projects

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: It's aim is to make a Basecamp style starred projects view on your Github home page. While working across many org's and repos, it can be a pain to keep track of what you're working on. So the idea is that you star a repo and it'll be available from your home page!
